divs: Sighting Detailswent for a walk outside with my girlfriend, around 9 -10 pm happend to look at the stars and saw two stars very brite, all of a sudden, one of them started to move a lil slowere than airplane speed, i could rule out airplane bcit was going so slow, and it was cloudy so its altitude low and it never went into a cloud, nore did it have red and green marker lights. so my first thought was that it was a falling star, it just slowly traveld over our heads in a north west direction, i live on the the corner of ********* and ******* rd, it seemed to be headed for ft. myers.
